hoenn_pokedex.name: Wailmer
hoenn_pokedex.description: It loves to startle people by forcefully spouting seawater out from its blowholes. It is known to bounce like a ball.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Wailord
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is the largest of all Pokémon. It can dive to a depth of almost 10,000 feet on only one breath.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Numel
hoenn_pokedex.description: The magma in its body can reach 2,200 degrees Fahrenheit. Its hump gets smaller when it is cold.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Camerupt
hoenn_pokedex.description: It has volcanoes on its back. If it is angered, the volcanoes erupt and spew molten lava.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Torkoal
hoenn_pokedex.description: It burns coal inside its shell for energy. It blows out black soot if it is endangered.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Spoink
hoenn_pokedex.description: It bounces constantly on its tail. The shock of its bouncing makes its heart pump.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Grumpig
hoenn_pokedex.description: It uses black pearls on its body to amplify its psychic power waves for gaining total control over its foe.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Spinda
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is said that no two Spinda have the same spot pattern. Its tottering step fouls the aim of foes.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Trapinch
hoenn_pokedex.description: It makes a conical pit in desert sand and lies in wait at the bottom for prey to tumble down.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Vibrava
hoenn_pokedex.description: It generates ultrasonic waves by violently vibrating its wings. After making its prey faint, it melts them with acid.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Flygon
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is known as 'The Desert Spirit.' Its flapping wings whip up a cloud of sand that covers it.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Cacnea
hoenn_pokedex.description: It lives in deserts. It can survive for 30 days on water stored in its body.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Cacturne
hoenn_pokedex.description: It becomes active at night, seeking prey that is exhausted from the day's desert heat.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Swablu
hoenn_pokedex.description: It has light and fluffy wings that are like cottony clouds. It is a tidy Pokémon that cleans things with its wings.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Altaria
hoenn_pokedex.description: It hums in a beautiful soprano voice. It flies among white clouds in the blue sky.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Zangoose
hoenn_pokedex.description: It has feuded with Seviper for many generations. Its sharp claws are its best weapon.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Seviper
hoenn_pokedex.description: It sharpens its sword-edged tail on rocks. It will not stop battling Zangoose.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Lunatone
hoenn_pokedex.description: It was discovered at the site of a meteor strike. It moves silently in the dark of night.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Solrock
hoenn_pokedex.description: A new species of Pokémon that is said to have fallen from the sun. It floats in the air and moves silently.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Barboach
hoenn_pokedex.description: Its body is covered with a slimy film. The film acts as a barrier to prevent germs in muddy water from entering the Barboach's body.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Whiscash
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is very territorial. It repels foes by setting off tremors that reach over a three-mile radius.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Corphish
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is a hardy Pokémon that can thrive in any environment. It has no opponents left in its territory.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Crawdaunt
hoenn_pokedex.description: A brutish Pokémon that has a violent nature. It is a ruffian that loves to pick on anyone.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Baltoy
hoenn_pokedex.description: It was discovered in ancient ruins. It moves by spinning on its single foot.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Claydol
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is said that it is a doll that was brought to life by a mysterious ray of light.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Lileep
hoenn_pokedex.description: It lived on the seafloor 100 million years ago. It became extinct in ancient times.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Cradily
hoenn_pokedex.description: It walks along the seafloor. It catches prey with its tentacles and melts them with digestive fluid.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Anorith
hoenn_pokedex.description: A Pokémon that was regenerated from a fossil. It lived in the sea and hunted with its pincers.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Armaldo
hoenn_pokedex.description: It went ashore after its entire body became covered with a hard armor. It is a ferocious predator.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Feebas
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is the shabbiest Pokémon of all. It is a hardy Pokémon that can thrive in any environment.
hoenn_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Milotic with high Beauty or via trade while holding a Prism Scale.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Milotic
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is said to be the most beautiful of all Pokémon. It has the power to calm any hostilities.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Castform
hoenn_pokedex.description: It alters its form and talent depending on the weather. The Pokémon changes with the temperature.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Kecleon
hoenn_pokedex.description: It can freely change its body's coloration. It is a mystery as to why it doesn't change the zigzag pattern on its belly.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Shuppet
hoenn_pokedex.description: It loves to feed on feelings like envy and malice. It will appear in a towns where such feelings run strong.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Banette
hoenn_pokedex.description: A doll that became a Pokémon over its grudge from being junked. It seeks the child that disowned it.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Duskull
hoenn_pokedex.description: It can pass through any wall no matter how thick. It is said that this Pokémon will spirit away bad children.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Dusclops
hoenn_pokedex.description: Its body is hollow. It is said that those who look into its body are sucked into the void.
hoenn_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Dusknoir via trade while holding a Reaper Cloth.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Tropius
hoenn_pokedex.description: It flies by flapping its broad leaves. The bunch of fruit that grows on its neck is a delicacy.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Chimecho
hoenn_pokedex.description: It uses the sucker on its head to hang from a tree or from eaves. It can cry endlessly.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Absol
hoenn_pokedex.description: It appears when it senses an impending natural disaster. As a result, it was mistaken as a doom-bringer.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Wynaut
hoenn_pokedex.description: It tends to move in a pack with others. They prefer dark places and squeeze together.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Snorunt
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is said that a home visited by a Snorunt will prosper. It can withstand cold of -150 degrees Fahrenheit.
hoenn_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Glalie or, if female, Froslass with a Dawn Stone.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Glalie
hoenn_pokedex.description: It has a body of ice that won't melt, even with fire. It can instantly freeze moisture in the atmosphere.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Spheal
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is completely covered with plushy fur. It is impervious to the cold, so it can swim in icy water.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Sealeo
hoenn_pokedex.description: It has a habit of spinning things on its nose. It can even spin a Spheal on its nose.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Walrein
hoenn_pokedex.description: It shatters drift ice with its powerful tusks. Its thick blubber repels attacks.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Clamperl
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is protected by a sturdy shell. It makes a single pearl during its lifetime.
hoenn_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Huntail (trade with Deep Sea Tooth) or Gorebyss (trade with Deep Sea Scale).

hoenn_pokedex.name: Huntail
hoenn_pokedex.description: It lives deep in the sea. It lures prey with its fish-shaped tail, then swallows them whole.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Gorebyss
hoenn_pokedex.description: Its body is built to withstand the enormous pressure of the deep sea. Its mouth is like a needle.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Relicanth
hoenn_pokedex.description: A Pokémon that was discovered during a deep-sea exploration. It has not changed in 100 million years.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Luvdisc
hoenn_pokedex.description: It lives in the warm seas of the tropics. This heart-shaped Pokémon earned its name by swimming after loving couples it spotted in the ocean's waves.
